{"title":"Hello World","date":"2018-07-21T13:10:51.000Z","author":"luoyayu","excerpt":"","slug":"2018-08-02-hello-world","comments":true,"dropcap":true,"tags":["hexo","life"],"categories":["Blog"],"updated":"2018-08-04T14:33:01.000Z","content":"<h3 id=\"测试-行内LaTeX\"><a href=\"#测试-行内LaTeX\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试 行内LaTeX\"></a>测试 行内LaTeX</h3><blockquote>\n<p>测试主题使用<strong>Angular</strong>搭建目前没有服务动态加载<strong>Mathjax</strong>解析脚本, 多校结束准备研究下前端基本框架</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>$x_i*y_j^2$ $y_{k}^{[0]}=A^{[0]}(\\omega_{\\frac{n}{2}}^k)$</p>\n<p>$\\displaystyle sum = \\sum_{i=1}^na_i$</p>\n<p>$\\mathbf{X}=\\begin{pmatrix}(\\mathbf{x}^{(1)})^T \\\\ (\\mathbf{x}^{(2)})^T \\\\ (\\mathbf{x}^{(3)})^T \\\\ \\cdot \\cdot \\cdot \\\\ (\\mathbf{x}^{(m)})^T\\end{pmatrix}$</p>\n<p>$\\Omega^TA\\Omega=\\begin{pmatrix}\\begin{pmatrix}a_1&amp;b_1 \\\\ -b_1&amp;a_1\\end{pmatrix}\\\\&amp;\\ddots\\\\&amp;&amp;\\begin{pmatrix}a_s&amp;b_s \\\\ -b_s&amp;a_s\\end{pmatrix}\\\\&amp;&amp;&amp;\\lambda_{2s+1}\\\\&amp;&amp;&amp;&amp;\\ddots\\\\&amp;&amp;&amp;&amp;&amp;\\lambda_n\\end{pmatrix}$<br>$\\begin{pmatrix}a&amp;*\\\\0&amp;b\\end{pmatrix}$</p>\n<h3 id=\"测试-行间公式\"><a href=\"#测试-行间公式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试 行间公式\"></a>测试 行间公式</h3><script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\\displaystyle y_k=y_k^{[0]}+w_n^ky_k^{[1]} =A^{[0]}(\\omega_{\\frac{n}{2}}^k)+w_n^kA^{[1]}(\\omega_{\\frac{n}{2}}^k)=A^{[0]}(\\omega_n^k)+w_n^kA^{[1]}(\\omega_n^k)=A(\\omega_n^k)</script><script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">H(y,\\hat{y}) = - \\frac{1}{n} \\sum_n \\sum_i y_{i,n} \\log (\\hat{y}_{i,n})</script><script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\n\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial t} = h^2 \\left( \\frac{\\partial^2 u}{\\partial x^2} + \\frac{\\partial^2 u}{\\partial y^2} + \\frac{\\partial^2 u}{\\partial z^2}\\right)</script><script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\nf\\left(\n    \\left[\n        \\frac{\n            1+\\left\\{x,y\\right\\}\n        }{\n        \\left(\n            \\frac{x}{y}+\\frac{y}{x}\n        \\right)\n        \\left(u+1\\right)\n        }+a\n    \\right]^{\\frac{3}{2}}\n\\right)</script><p>来自多校<a href=\"http://acm.hdu.edu.cn/showproblem.php?pid=6339\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">round-4 H.Eat Cards, Have Fun</a>无情公式推导</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\\displaystyle \n\\begin{aligned} \n\\sum_{k = 1} ^ {\\infty} & {(1 - (1 - p) ^ k) ^ l ((1 - p) ^ k) ^ {i - 1 - l} p (1 - p) ^ {k - 1} (1 - (1 - p) ^ {k - 1}) ^ r ((1 - p) ^ {k - 1}) ^ {n - i - r}}  \\\\  \n= & p \\sum_{k = 1} ^ {\\infty} {(1 - p) ^ {k(i - 1 - l) + k - 1 + (k - 1)(n - i - r)} \\sum_{x = 0} ^ {l} {\\binom{l}{x} (-1) ^ x (1 - p) ^ {xk}} \\sum_{y = 0} ^ {r} {\\binom{r}{y} (-1) ^ y (1 - p) ^ {y(k - 1)}}} \\\\ \n= & p \\sum_{x = 0} ^ {l} \\sum_{y = 0} ^ {r} {(-1) ^ {x + y} \\binom{l}{x} \\binom{r}{y} \\sum_{k = 1} ^ {\\infty} {(1 - p) ^ {k(i - 1 - l) + k - 1 + (k - 1)(n - i - r) + xk + y(k - 1)}}} \\\\ \n= & p \\sum_{x = 0} ^ {l} \\sum_{y = 0} ^ {r} {(-1) ^ {x + y} \\binom{l}{x} \\binom{r}{y} \\sum_{k = 0} ^ {\\infty} {(1 - p) ^ {k (n - l - r + x + y) + (i - 1 - l + x)}}} \\\\ \n= & p \\sum_{x = 0} ^ {l} \\sum_{y = 0} ^ {r} {(-1) ^ {x + y} \\binom{l}{x} \\binom{r}{y} \\frac{(1 - p) ^ {i - 1 - l + x}} {1 - (1 - p) ^ {n - l - r + x + y}}} \n\\end{aligned}</script><script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\n\\require{enclose}\\begin{array}{}\n\\enclose{horizontalstrike}{x+y}\\\\\n\\enclose{horizontalstrike}{x*y}\\\\\n\\end{array}</script><h3 id=\"测试-cpp\"><a href=\"#测试-cpp\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试 cpp\"></a>测试 cpp</h3><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br><span class=\"line\">74</span><br><span class=\"line\">75</span><br><span class=\"line\">76</span><br><span class=\"line\">77</span><br><span class=\"line\">78</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"built_in\">std</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//题意:给出括号序列染色要求</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/*1.括号要么不被染色要么染成红或蓝色</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> *2.相邻的括号要染色保持不同</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> *3.相匹配的括号有且只有一个被染色</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// dp[l][r][x][y]为[l,r]表示给[l,r]染色且端点l染x色，右端点r染y色</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// &lt;0,1,2&gt;分别为&lt;plain, red, blue&gt; if &lt;l,r&gt; is matched</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// ,那么由去掉这个嵌套的dp[l+1][r-1][x][y]转移出dp[l][r][x][y]枚举l+1,r-1的颜色</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* i-&gt;l+1; j-&gt;r-1;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * if(i!=1) dp[l][r][1][0]=(dp[l][r][1][0] + dp[l+1][r-1][i][j])%mod;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * if(i!=2) dp[l][r][2][0]=(dp[l][r][2][0] + dp[l+1][r-1][i][j])%mod;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * if(j!=1) dp[l][r][0][1]=(dp[l][r][0][1] + dp[l+1][r-1][i][j])%mod;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * if(j!=2) dp[l][r][0][2]=(dp[l][r][0][2] + dp[l+1][r-1][i][j])%mod;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// if &lt;l,r&gt; isn't matched 那么可以找到和l匹配的括号位置mid,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 求出dp[l][mid][][]和dp[mid+1][r][][]枚举l,mid,mid+1,r这四个位置的颜色i,j,x,y</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 有转移方程 if(j*x==0||j!=x) </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// dp[l][r][i][y] = (dp[l][r][i][y] + dp[l][mid][i][j] * dp[mid+1][r][x][y]%mod)%mod;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> ll;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> maxn = <span class=\"number\">700</span> + <span class=\"number\">7</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> mod = <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>(<span class=\"number\">1e9</span> + <span class=\"number\">7</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> belong[maxn];</span><br><span class=\"line\">ll dp[maxn][maxn][<span class=\"number\">3</span>][<span class=\"number\">3</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">char</span> ss[maxn];</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">dfs</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> l, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> r)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (r - l == <span class=\"number\">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        dp[l][r][<span class=\"number\">0</span>][<span class=\"number\">1</span>] = dp[l][r][<span class=\"number\">0</span>][<span class=\"number\">2</span>] = dp[l][r][<span class=\"number\">1</span>][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] = dp[l][r][<span class=\"number\">2</span>][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (belong[l] == r) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        dfs(l + <span class=\"number\">1</span>, r - <span class=\"number\">1</span>);  <span class=\"comment\">//一直递归到小区间处理</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; <span class=\"number\">3</span>; i++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; j &lt; <span class=\"number\">3</span>; j++) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (i != <span class=\"number\">1</span>) dp[l][r][<span class=\"number\">1</span>][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] = (dp[l][r][<span class=\"number\">1</span>][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] + dp[l + <span class=\"number\">1</span>][r - <span class=\"number\">1</span>][i][j]) % mod;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (i != <span class=\"number\">2</span>) dp[l][r][<span class=\"number\">2</span>][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] = (dp[l][r][<span class=\"number\">2</span>][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] + dp[l + <span class=\"number\">1</span>][r - <span class=\"number\">1</span>][i][j]) % mod;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (j != <span class=\"number\">1</span>) dp[l][r][<span class=\"number\">0</span>][<span class=\"number\">1</span>] = (dp[l][r][<span class=\"number\">0</span>][<span class=\"number\">1</span>] + dp[l + <span class=\"number\">1</span>][r - <span class=\"number\">1</span>][i][j]) % mod;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (j != <span class=\"number\">2</span>) dp[l][r][<span class=\"number\">0</span>][<span class=\"number\">2</span>] = (dp[l][r][<span class=\"number\">0</span>][<span class=\"number\">2</span>] + dp[l + <span class=\"number\">1</span>][r - <span class=\"number\">1</span>][i][j]) % mod;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> mid = belong[l];</span><br><span class=\"line\">        dfs(l, mid);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        dfs(mid + <span class=\"number\">1</span>, r);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; <span class=\"number\">3</span>; i++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; j &lt; <span class=\"number\">3</span>; j++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> x = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; x &lt; <span class=\"number\">3</span>; x++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> y = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; y &lt; <span class=\"number\">3</span>; y++)  &#123;<span class=\"comment\">//&lt;i,j&gt;, &lt;x,y&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (j * x != <span class=\"number\">0</span> &amp;&amp; j == x) <span class=\"keyword\">continue</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        dp[l][r][i][y] = (dp[l][r][i][y] + dp[l][mid][i][j] * dp[mid + <span class=\"number\">1</span>][r][x][y] % mod) %mod;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> (<span class=\"built_in\">scanf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%s\"</span>, ss) != EOF) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> len = <span class=\"built_in\">strlen</span>(ss);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; len; i++)  <span class=\"comment\">//处理匹配</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (ss[i] == <span class=\"string\">'('</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> cnt = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j = i; j &lt; len; j++) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (ss[j] == <span class=\"string\">'('</span>) cnt++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> cnt--;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (cnt == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        belong[i] = j;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">memset</span>(dp, <span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">sizeof</span>(dp));</span><br><span class=\"line\">        dfs(<span class=\"number\">0</span>, len - <span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ll ans = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; <span class=\"number\">3</span>; i++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; j &lt; <span class=\"number\">3</span>; j++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">                ans = (ans + dp[<span class=\"number\">0</span>][len - <span class=\"number\">1</span>][i][j]) % mod;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%lld\\n\"</span>, ans);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"测试-折叠golang代码\"><a href=\"#测试-折叠golang代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试 折叠golang代码\"></a>测试 折叠golang代码</h3><details>\n<figure class=\"highlight go\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br><span class=\"line\">74</span><br><span class=\"line\">75</span><br><span class=\"line\">76</span><br><span class=\"line\">77</span><br><span class=\"line\">78</span><br><span class=\"line\">79</span><br><span class=\"line\">80</span><br><span class=\"line\">81</span><br><span class=\"line\">82</span><br><span class=\"line\">83</span><br><span class=\"line\">84</span><br><span class=\"line\">85</span><br><span class=\"line\">86</span><br><span class=\"line\">87</span><br><span class=\"line\">88</span><br><span class=\"line\">89</span><br><span class=\"line\">90</span><br><span class=\"line\">91</span><br><span class=\"line\">92</span><br><span class=\"line\">93</span><br><span class=\"line\">94</span><br><span class=\"line\">95</span><br><span class=\"line\">96</span><br><span class=\"line\">97</span><br><span class=\"line\">98</span><br><span class=\"line\">99</span><br><span class=\"line\">100</span><br><span class=\"line\">101</span><br><span class=\"line\">102</span><br><span class=\"line\">103</span><br><span class=\"line\">104</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">package</span> main</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> (</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">\"bufio\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">\"fmt\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">\"io\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">\"log\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">\"math\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">\"net/http\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">\"os\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">\"strconv\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">\"strings\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">\"sync\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> mu sync.Mutex <span class=\"comment\">// 共享变量</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> count <span class=\"keyword\">int</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// ServerStart 开始服务器监听</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"title\">ServerStart</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfmt.Println(<span class=\"string\">\"WEB START, HTTP LISTEN PORT 2333\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\thttp.HandleFunc(<span class=\"string\">\"/\"</span>, UpdateCounterAndPrintMore)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\thttp.HandleFunc(<span class=\"string\">\"/count\"</span>, counter)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\thttp.HandleFunc(<span class=\"string\">\"/drawfun\"</span>, HandleQuest)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\thttp.HandleFunc(<span class=\"string\">\"/code\"</span>, ShowCode)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tlog.Fatal(http.ListenAndServe(<span class=\"string\">\"10.0.0.103:2333\"</span>, <span class=\"literal\">nil</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"title\">counter</span><span class=\"params\">(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)</span></span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tmu.Lock()</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfmt.Fprintf(w, <span class=\"string\">\"Count %d\\n\"</span>, count)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tmu.Unlock()</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// UpdateCounterAndPrintMore 跟新计数器状态并且打印请求头更多的内容</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"title\">UpdateCounterAndPrintMore</span><span class=\"params\">(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)</span></span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tmu.Lock() <span class=\"comment\">//共享变量加锁</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tcount++</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tmu.Unlock()</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// fmt.Fprintf(w, \"URL.Path=%q\\n\", r.URL.Path)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// Request 结构体</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfmt.Fprintf(w, <span class=\"string\">\"%s %s %s\\n\"</span>, r.Method, r.URL, r.Proto)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span> k, v := <span class=\"keyword\">range</span> r.Header &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tfmt.Fprintf(w, <span class=\"string\">\"Header[%q]=%q\\n\"</span>, k, v)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfmt.Fprintf(w, <span class=\"string\">\"Host=%q\\n\"</span>, r.Host)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfmt.Fprintf(w, <span class=\"string\">\"RemoteAdd=%q\\n\"</span>, r.RemoteAddr)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> err := r.ParseForm(); err != <span class=\"literal\">nil</span> &#123; <span class=\"comment\">// 限制作用域</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tlog.Print(err)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span> k, v := <span class=\"keyword\">range</span> r.Form &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tfmt.Fprintf(w, <span class=\"string\">\"Form[%q]=%q\\n\"</span>, k, v)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//HandleQuest 处理URL中的?引起的请求</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"title\">HandleQuest</span><span class=\"params\">(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)</span></span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tw.Header().Set(<span class=\"string\">\"Content-Type\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"image/svg+xml\"</span>) <span class=\"comment\">// 写svg类型文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// width, height, cells, funstring, angle</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tquery := r.URL.RawQuery</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tQ := strings.Split(query, <span class=\"string\">\"?\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\twidth, height, cells, angle = <span class=\"number\">600</span>, <span class=\"number\">320</span>, <span class=\"number\">100</span>, math.Pi/<span class=\"number\">6</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tFunctionstring = <span class=\"string\">\"sin(sqrt(x*x+y*y))/sqrt(x*x+y*y)\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span> _, q := <span class=\"keyword\">range</span> Q &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">switch</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">case</span> strings.HasPrefix(q, <span class=\"string\">\"width=\"</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\twidth, _ = strconv.Atoi(q[<span class=\"number\">6</span>:])</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">case</span> strings.HasPrefix(q, <span class=\"string\">\"height=\"</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\theight, _ = strconv.Atoi(q[<span class=\"number\">7</span>:])</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">case</span> strings.HasPrefix(q, <span class=\"string\">\"cells=\"</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tcells, _ = strconv.Atoi(q[<span class=\"number\">6</span>:])</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">case</span> strings.HasPrefix(q, <span class=\"string\">\"angle=\"</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tangle, _ = strconv.ParseFloat(q[<span class=\"number\">6</span>:], <span class=\"number\">64</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">// angle /= 360</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">case</span> strings.HasPrefix(q, <span class=\"string\">\"func=\"</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tFunctionstring = q[<span class=\"number\">5</span>:]</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tsin30, cos30 = math.Sin(angle), math.Cos(angle)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfmt.Printf(<span class=\"string\">\"请求 width=%d height=%d cells=%d angle=%f\\n\"</span>, width, height, cells, angle)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfmt.Printf(<span class=\"string\">\"函数: %s\\n\"</span>, Functionstring)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tf, _ := os.Create(<span class=\"string\">\"fun_sample.svg\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\twg.Add(cells * cells)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tSurface(f)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\twg.Wait()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfmt.Fprintln(f, <span class=\"string\">\"&lt;/svg&gt;\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfmt.Println(<span class=\"string\">\"完成绘制任务\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tf, _ = os.Open(<span class=\"string\">\"fun_sample.svg\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tio.Copy(w, f)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tf.Close()</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// ShowCode 响应源码请求</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"title\">ShowCode</span><span class=\"params\">(w http.ResponseWriter, f *http.Request)</span></span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfileF, _ := os.Open(<span class=\"string\">\"code.txt\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tinput := bufio.NewScanner(fileF)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span> input.Scan() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tfmt.Fprintln(w, input.Text())</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n</details>\n\n<h3 id=\"测试-Gist\"><a href=\"#测试-Gist\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试 Gist\"></a>测试 Gist</h3><blockquote>\n<p>测试主题暂时不支持</p>\n</blockquote>\n<script src=\"//gist.github.com/5bd5a2f0c126d8f60833973ca4b41749.js?file=find_cycle_in_graph.cpp\"></script>\n<h3 id=\"测试-Include-Code\"><a href=\"#测试-Include-Code\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试 Include Code\"></a>测试 Include Code</h3><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><figcaption><span> 莫队算法-小Z的袜子</span><a href=\"/downloads/code/Mo.cpp\">view raw</a></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"built_in\">std</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">define</span> clr(a, b) memset(a, b, sizeof(a));</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">define</span> debug(x) cout &lt;&lt; #x &lt;&lt; <span class=\"meta-string\">\" = \"</span> &lt;&lt; x &lt;&lt; endl;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">define</span> y2 Y2</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* 莫队算法</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * BZOJ 2038 小Z的袜子</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * 设查询的区间长度为n, ANS = \\frac{\\sum_{i=0}^{color_n} sum[i]*(sum[i]-1) }{n(n-1)}</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * 莫队算法巧妙的做离线SORT，可以在两个询问之间快速做状态跳转。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * l指针向左移动一个单位，r指针向右移动一个单位，这些状态都可以在O(1)时间完成跳转</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * 其优化基于分块的双关键词：若l在同块，则以r作为排序关键词；若l不在同块，将l作为排序关键词</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * 思路：</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">*/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> ll;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> maxn = <span class=\"number\">5e5</span> + <span class=\"number\">7</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">Mo</span> {</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> l, r ,idx;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tll A, B;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}q[maxn]; <span class=\"comment\">// 询问</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">inline</span> ll <span class=\"title\">S</span><span class=\"params\">(ll x )</span> </span>{ <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> x*x; }</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> n, m, color[maxn];</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> block_size, belong[maxn];</span><br><span class=\"line\">ll sum[maxn], ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">bool</span> <span class=\"title\">cmp</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">const</span> Mo &amp;a, <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> Mo &amp;b)</span> </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> belong[a.l]==belong[b.l] ? a.r &lt; b.r : a.l &lt; b.l;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">bool</span> <span class=\"title\">CMP</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">const</span> Mo &amp;a, <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> Mo &amp;b)</span> </span>{ <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> a.idx &lt; b.idx; }</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">inline</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">revise</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> x, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> add)</span> </span>{ <span class=\"comment\">// O(1) 转移</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tans -= S(sum[color[x]]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tsum[color[x]] += add; <span class=\"comment\">// 第x种颜色加上add个</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tans += S(sum[color[x]]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span> </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"built_in\">std</span>::ios::sync_with_stdio(<span class=\"literal\">false</span>), <span class=\"built_in\">cin</span>.tie(<span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"built_in\">cin</span> &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tblock_size = <span class=\"built_in\">sqrt</span>(n);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++) <span class=\"built_in\">cin</span> &gt;&gt; color[i], belong[i]=i/block_size+<span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i&lt;=m;i++) <span class=\"built_in\">cin</span> &gt;&gt; q[i].l &gt;&gt; q[i].r, q[i].idx = i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tsort(q+<span class=\"number\">1</span>, q+m+<span class=\"number\">1</span>, cmp);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> l=<span class=\"number\">1</span>, r=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i&lt;=m;i++) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(l&lt;q[i].l) revise(l,  <span class=\"number\">-1</span>), l++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(l&gt;q[i].l) revise(l<span class=\"number\">-1</span>, <span class=\"number\">1</span>), l--;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(r&lt;q[i].r) revise(r+<span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"number\">1</span>), r++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(r&gt;q[i].r) revise(r,  <span class=\"number\">-1</span>), r--;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(q[i].l == q[i].r) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tq[i].A =<span class=\"number\">0</span>, q[i].B = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">continue</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t}</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> N = q[i].r - q[i].l + <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tq[i].A = ans - N;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tq[i].B = <span class=\"number\">1L</span>L*N*(N<span class=\"number\">-1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tll gcd = __gcd(q[i].A, q[i].B);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tq[i].A /= gcd, q[i].B /=gcd;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t}</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tsort(q+<span class=\"number\">1</span>, q+m+<span class=\"number\">1</span>, CMP);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i&lt;=m;i++) <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; q[i].A &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"/\"</span> &lt;&lt; q[i].B &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"测试-引用块\"><a href=\"#测试-引用块\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试 引用块\"></a>测试 引用块</h3><blockquote><p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Pellentesque hendrerit lacus ut purus iaculis feugiat. Sed nec tempor elit, quis 