ss=\"regexp\">/^\\s*(&lt;p&gt;\\s*)?\\[ \\]\\s*/i</span>, <span class=\"string\">'&lt;input type=\"checkbox\" disabled&gt;&lt;/input&gt; '</span>).replace(<span class=\"regexp\">/^\\s*(&lt;p&gt;\\s*)?\\[x\\]\\s*/i</span>, <span class=\"string\">'&lt;input type=\"checkbox\" checked disabled&gt;&lt;/input&gt; '</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    result = <span class=\"string\">'&lt;li style=\"list-style: none\"&gt;'</span> + text + <span class=\"string\">'&lt;/li&gt;\\n'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    result = <span class=\"string\">'&lt;li&gt;'</span> + text + <span class=\"string\">'&lt;/li&gt;\\n'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> result;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"就这样，开始吧\"><a href=\"#就这样，开始吧\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"就这样，开始吧\"></a>就这样，开始吧</h3><ul>\n<li style=\"list-style: none\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> 迁移WordPress至Hexo。</li>\n<li style=\"list-style: none\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> 每周至少一篇记录生活，反思现状。</li>\n<li style=\"list-style: none\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> 至少把这个主题的框架搞懂了。</li>\n<li style=\"list-style: none\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> 开学跟进机器学习，现阶段打好ACM，拿铁不想喝了。</li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"Learning Golang I","slug":"2018-08-03-learning Go"},"link":"/2018/07/21"}